asset.title: 2012 - 2013 Honda Civic SI 2.4L & 2013 - 2014 Acura ILX 2.4L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2012 - 2013 Honda Civic SI 2.4L or 2013 - 2014 Acura ILX 2.4L.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-1019TS

K&N 69-1019TS air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 10.5 horsepower at 5400 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 69-1019TS fits the following: 
2014 ACURA ILX 2.4L L4 F/I - All 
2013 HONDA CIVIC SI 2.4L L4 F/I - All 
2013 ACURA ILX 2.4L L4 F/I - All 
2012 HONDA CIVIC SI 2.4L L4 F/I - All 
 
Go to http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-1019TS for an up to date application list.

To search for your own vehicle's corresponding cold air intake and air filter visit
http://www.KNfilters.com
